node.text:
New listing! Thrilled to market this epic Montecito Mission style estate in Westlake Village, Ca. Absolutely remarkable custom showplace on a prime 30,000 square foot usable lot in North Ranch. A very special setting with 350 feet of frontage to the North Ranch golf course. Explosive unobstructed panoramic views like no other! Completely reimagined inside and out with the finest finishes. Spanning 4700 square feet with truly the best golf course views North Ranch has to offer. Features include 4 bedrooms, 4 baths, library, wine room, custom wood detailed ceilings, and so much more all with an incredible open concept floorplan throughout. The resort quality grounds are second to none! Custom pool and spa, private babbling Brook, oak tree forest, massive manicured lawns and much more! A very special offering!

$4,500,000

node.text:
I wanted to thank everyone that followed my Instagram story for the past 10 days. I greatly appreciate each and every amazing dm that I received. It was awesome to receive so many messages that told me how much you enjoyed my posts and so many more that have asked me to repost. I generally like to only post real estate pics,  but here goes my top 10 moments. I wish I could post 100 more. From the bottom of my heart I want to thank the great people of South Africa and all the amazing staff of the @royalmalewane ! There is no place I enjoy more in the world. I also want to thank my Travel agent @floridaafrican for booking us a flawless experience. The third one Andre has booked for us. I am already looking forward to next year! This one was special. My wife and I were able to take this Safari with our best friends and that made it that much more special. Please enjoy the posts and let me know what your think and what your favorites are in the comments below. Thanks again!
#southafrica #safari #safarilife #africa #lions #elephants #leopard #rhino #africanwilddog #wilddogs #giraffe #myhappyplace

node.text:
Take another look at my world class listing in beautiful Ojai, Ca. A truly epic one of a kind 3600 acre cattle ranch famously known as Black Mountain Ranch. Features and amenities rarely seen. The primary residence spans over 13,000 square feet and has been designed and built with the absolute finest finishes. There are numerous structures including guest houses, staff quarters, a 7200 square foot auto museum, a 9300 square foot hay barn and much more. The property also provides  35 miles of private trails, private fishing lake, tennis court, shooting range, 6200 square foot carriage house and so much more. With complete privacy, 63 continuous parcels and unmatched views, Black Mountain Ranch is unquestionably Southern California’s premier ranch estate. 

$100,000,000

node.text:
Flashback to January of 2020 when I closed the very first luxury home in The Estates At North Ranch. This has been a very special community for me to list and and sell and this was the very first one. Since this deal we have completely sold out of phase 1 and Phase 2. 10 sales in all. The third and final phase has broken ground and I look forward to marketing these last 5 estates in the beginning of 2022. The Estates At North Ranch in Ventura County’s newest gated community located in the city of Westlake Village. What a sensational development loved by all the new residents. Developed by my lifelong friend @ronlogan123 , built by @adroitcustomhomes and designed by @sophieidan , these custom estates are truly epic. This first home was 5500 square feet and sold for $4,815,000
